				</link>
				<link label="Reporting a bug" url="http://org.eclipse.ui.intro/showHelpTopic?id=/org.mwc.debrief.help/html/legacy/debrief_feedback.html&amp;embedTarget=page-content" id="report_bug">
					<text>Learn how to report Debrief-relatedproblems</text>
